WEBVTT

00:05:27.976 --> 00:05:33.781
because war kills people
by robbing them of their clinics,

00:05:33.805 --> 00:05:34.982
of their hospitals,

00:05:35.006 --> 00:05:36.870
of their supply chains.

00:05:36.894 --> 00:05:40.485
Their doctors are targeted, are killed;
they're on the run.

00:05:40.509 --> 00:05:44.428
And more invisible
and yet more deadly is the destruction

00:05:44.452 --> 00:05:47.988
of the health governance institutions
and their finances.

00:05:49.118 --> 00:05:52.357
So this is really not
surprising at all to me.

00:05:53.790 --> 00:05:56.340
But what is surprising
and somewhat dismaying,

00:05:56.364 --> 00:06:00.338
is how little impact this insight has had,